  Scenario A: Moab & Its Fringe
  
  This scenario concentrates future growth within Moab and in those areas
  already characterized by urban development. It implements a “Grow
  up, not out” philosophy, tailored to fit the metro area and acknowledge
  existing infrastructure investment and programmed projects. It recognizes
  that much of Spanish Valley is already platted, but prioritizes investing in
  water and transportation infrastructure for projects near the center of
  Moab’s urban area.
  
