  | --- | --- | --- | --- |
  | Density Bonus (Units/Acre) | Unit Increase | % Increase | Workforce Housing Units | Density Bonus (Units/Acre) | Unit Increase | % Increase | Workforce Housing Units |
  | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
  | SLR, Small Lot Residential | 5 | 8.0 | 3.0 | 60% | 2 | 9.5 | 4.5 | 90% | 4 |
